{"id":109452,"type":6,"name":"The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies","name_cn":"霍比特人3：五军之战","date":"2014-12-17","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/aa/2d/109452_Mgzm6.jpg","rating":{"rank":738,"total":251,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":7,"6":25,"7":75,"8":95,"9":26,"10":19},"score":7.6},"summary":"　　被吵醒的史矛革大闹长湖镇，最终为人类巴德（卢克·伊万斯 Luke Evans 饰）射杀。索林·橡木盾（理查德·阿米蒂奇 Richard Armitage 饰）多年的夙愿终于实现，孤山埃尔波尔重新回到矮人手中。然而这位矮人王子仿佛被史矛革的贪婪和堆成山的黄金迷惑了心窍，他 疯狂地搜寻象征王位的阿肯宝石，不仅撕毁了付给长湖镇报酬的约定，更拒绝了精灵王（李·佩斯 Lee Pace 饰）索要本族国宝的要求，为此导致三族的战争一触即发。与此同时，苍白半兽人阿索格率领大军浩浩荡荡向孤山逼近。得知消息的灰袍巫师甘道夫（伊恩·麦凯伦 Ian McKellen 饰）从中调停斡旋，而被索林视为唯一朋友的霍比特人比尔博·巴金斯（马丁·弗里曼 Martin John C. Freeman 饰）则掌握着中土命运的关键。五军会战，爆发在即！ \r\n　　本片根据J.R.R·托尔金的同名原著改编，为霍比特人系列的最后一部。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>霍比特人3：五军之战</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/7590\">J.R.R. Tolkien</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/42414\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Peter Jackson</a>、<a href=\"/person/34596\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Andy Serkis</a></li><li><span>编剧: </span>Fran Walsh、Philippa Boyens、<a href=\"/person/42414\">Peter Jackson</a>、<a href=\"/person/49728\">Guillermo del Toro</a></li><li><span>制片人/制作人: </span><a href=\"/person/42414\">Peter Jackson</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/40610\">Martin Freeman</a>、<a href=\"/person/34628\">Ian McKellen</a>、<a href=\"/person/42386\">Richard Armitage</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/29179\">Orlando Bloom</a>、Evangeline Lilly、<a href=\"/person/56717\">Luke Evans</a>、<a href=\"/person/17161\">Benedict Cumberbatch</a>、<a href=\"/person/17669\">Lee Pace</a>、<a href=\"/person/47053\">Graham McTavish</a>、Ken Stott、Aidan Turner、Dean O'Gorman、Manu Bennett、Mark Hadlow、Jed Brophy、Adam Brown、John Callen、Peter Hambleton、William Kircher、<a href=\"/person/42413\">James Nesbitt</a>、Stephen Hunter、<a href=\"/person/42380\">Cate Blanchett</a>、<a href=\"/person/40558\">Hugo Weaving</a>、<a href=\"/person/34666\">Christopher Lee</a>、<a href=\"/person/42292\">Sylvester McCoy</a>、John Tui